[38:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that it has never seen in its training data before. So for example, it needs to learn this visual puzzle and then be able to solve this. The thing is most AI models, they don\'t actually learn new things after training. So historically,'

[39:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it\'s been really hard for, you know, even the top AI models to solve these ARGI benchmarks as you can see over here. But notice that for this new TRM model, it scored even better than some'

[39:13] [scene:talk]
